and vegetables and foods,

00:14:48.700 --> 00:14:53.290 align:middle line:84%
and even have a fish
pond for your own tilapia

00:14:53.290 --> 00:14:54.910 align:middle line:90%
right there in your home.

00:14:54.910 --> 00:14:58.240 align:middle line:84%
>>REYNOLDS: Yeah, I
think that's the thing.

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:03.370 align:middle line:84%
It's the thinking
of this is to really

00:15:03.370 --> 00:15:05.200 align:middle line:90%
transcend infrastructure.

00:15:05.200 --> 00:15:07.660 align:middle line:84%
