disposal of their garbage.

00:15:16.240 --> 00:15:21.460 align:middle line:84%
If we can make this part of
the everyday living of people,

00:15:21.460 --> 00:15:25.690 align:middle line:84%
we've cut down their
dependence on infrastructure,

00:15:25.690 --> 00:15:29.890 align:middle line:84%
if not eliminated
it, and, therefore,

00:15:29.890 --> 00:15:33.850 align:middle line:84%
put them on a different
level in terms of economy

00:15:33.850 --> 00:15:37.510 align:middle line:84%
because the economy,
