pathway for sustenance that

00:15:50.470 --> 00:15:52.180 align:middle line:90%
has nothing to do with economy.

00:15:52.180 --> 00:15:53.140 align:middle line:90%
The sun is there.

00:15:53.140 --> 00:15:54.310 align:middle line:90%
The rain is there.

00:15:54.310 --> 00:15:57.190 align:middle line:84%
The biology and the physics
