00:15:57.190 --> 00:15:59.170 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to go
through an economy

00:15:59.170 --> 00:16:02.230 align:middle line:84%
to get at them for
your sustenance.

00:16:02.230 --> 00:16:05.440 align:middle line:84%
So we're trying to make these
